import React from 'react'

import Capa5 from '../capas/rises.png'

const PlaylistSongs =[

    {
        id: 2, 
        cover: Capa1, 
        name: 'Only One Who Knows', 
        author: 'Arctic Monkeys', 
        durantion: '3:04',

    {

    {
